org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent

Interface FromXContentBuilder<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlobStoreIndexShardSnapshot, BlobStoreIndexShardSnapshots, IndexMetaData, MetaData, Snapshot

    public interface FromXContentBuilder<T>
    Indicates that the class supports XContent deserialization. This interface is similar to what StreamableReader does, only it works with XContent serialization instead of binary serialization.
